				\begin{document}$$\sqrt{{VW}}$$\end{document} are the energy of two states and their coupling constant. The eigenvalues are thus expressed as E±=E1+E22±E1−E222+VW\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
				\usepackage{amsfonts}
